'''Isabel''' is [[Jonathan Bright|Jonathan Bright's]] producer.

==History==
Isabel was in a helicopter with Jonathan during a lightning storm when the helicopter was struck by lightning, leading to a crash landing. Isabel had only minor injuries, but was worried about Jonathan, whose leg had been impaled. The firefighters were able to remove the door and free Isabel. They loaded her into a gurney and took her to Seattle Pres.

==Career==
She's a producer at 3 News.
